description:
Here are Hectors notes regarding tonight's episodes.



First of all, why is this labeled Episodes 37a and 37b?

Well, tonight BBAU decided to try a new trick.

They switched channels after half an hour from the main network "Channel 9" to their offshoot one "GO".

All of this was due to a live football match.

So, in order to upload them both to you, I decided not to attempt joining them and absolutely delete them by mistake!

They are labeled 37a and 37b because if the website chooses to make them 2 different episodes,

it's less confusing then having to episode 38's!

If anyone is confused, place a comment and will try to re-explain my decision!
